{"tid":1423010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非全面進場］下一次嘅和理非行動係809萬人接機","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:04:03.000Z","uid":177213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6dd472259f2ce6ec72e22aa26f5beab13ac382","tid":1423010,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"經過琴日一役 前線要好好休息 多謝你哋為香港嘅付出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家係和理非全面進場嘅時候  大家可以去機場接機 ！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動唔可以成日搞 所以完全冇癱瘓機場嘅打算<br />\n<br />\n最後麻煩大家多啲開post宣傳下今次活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n809機場行動tg<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/My9aBxbFMux9J6siqYRxNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMy9aBxbFMux9J6siqYRxNw&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=07bef41b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/My9aBxbFMux9J6siqYRxNw</a><br />\n<br />\nChannel link:<br />\n@Terminal809 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n承接上一篇文：<br />\n<br />\n「809萬人接機」機場行動將不會申請不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394365</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區<br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n<br />\n是次活動旨在把和理非與前線帶到最安全嘅地方暫時放下gear聚集與休息，大家一齊走下去<br />\n和平，理性，非暴力<br />\n<br />\n和理非可以為前線爭取到時間休息，前線都可以趁呢段時間預備裝備及制定新策略；<br />\n同時令整場抗爭運動不冷化，又不會勞民傷財，更可以令到和理非勇武徹底做到一個交接嘅效果，互相扶持接力<br />\n<br />\n機場優勢 ：<br />\n<br />\n1. 限制警方武力：如唔可以投放催淚彈、開槍，否則會導致機場停飛、引發消防灑水系統、影響機場運作及評級等各種問題。<br />\n2. 唔可以暴力驅散，避免驚嚇或誤傷旅客，引起國際風波。<br />\n3. 機場特警表明，只要不入禁區、不入跑道，則唔會出手。<br />\n4. 警方不能夠封島，因為會阻礙乘客出入、油車及貨物運輸。<br />\n5. 機場乃本港重要財產及主要基建，更直接影響國際形象，於各方面較其他地方能保障發聲人士安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實際有咩行動？<br />\n<br />\n大家可以拖喼可以唔拖 ， 拖篋嘅話會可以貼上資訊單張 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於冇申請不反對通知書，我哋唔可以叫口號同舉牌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係如果有過萬人喺嗰度 叫口號同佢牌又捉得到邊個？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以今次行動究竟有咩可以做係人數決定一切 麻煩各位一齊嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔想去到之後咩都冇得做 淨係貼資料喺背囊或者身上 咁就麻煩要更加多人出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次亦都係一個實驗 睇吓唔申請不反對通知書但係夠多人嘅話 會唔會都可以做到申請不反對通知書嘅效果 同時又唔俾人趕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋認為淨係搞一日效果太細 搞三日先會有較大影響力 <br />\n<br />\n順便都實驗一下有冇行動係可以連續一日以上<br />\n<br />\n咁多位 9/8 ， 10/8 ， 11/8 見！<br />\n<br />\n如果你冇時間去曬三日 淨係去一日都得！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋沒有大台<br />\n809連活動名都係投票出來嘅<br />\n當日都係所有行動將交給在場人士投票決定<br />\n總之成個行動都係大家嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oiPXTAn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoiPXTAn.png&h=397db23d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PaEwX12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPaEwX12.png&h=f7f5b53d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNKdrVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNKdrVn.png&h=a34be60f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UyHeVOJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyHeVOJ.png&h=ac7a70d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7Vj6Vo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7Vj6Vo.png&h=fead2d29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nnvj6Vp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnvj6Vp.png&h=e7ed79e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uTnOfOK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuTnOfOK.png&h=a22a086c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c19c3c9652c1654261b4f5dac6246c700b8385c","tid":1423010,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"[回應同警察傾計個post] 警世，終於知道點解連登仔咁易比人帶到風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8c782f36b855958e874c32dc967af1f3238019b","tid":1423010,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推</span>"},{"pid":"39a27cbc933ba3ebd7b1d6bdc99313f0942ab72d","tid":1423010,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7704877afa4bf7405a6e48d3b9e14323af34c816","tid":1423010,"uid":52341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc4490e3e51ce72b125f9ee15f6df3bc23c1b5b","tid":1423010,"uid":275887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"真心感激 前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ad48ed6934b44f3a83e144138916c1523aac48","tid":1423010,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"推晒所有機場post<br />\n<br />\n懇請航空業業界發動罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426710</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8月6日深水埗無差別拘捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425299</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"49f1a327366598e2256b7f69ad1f6bb0ee13a003","tid":1423010